982
00:57:47.147 --> 00:57:48.432
Well, isn't that interesting?

983
00:57:48.857 --> 00:57:50.472
I'll take this back
to Washington with me.


984
00:57:50.650 --> 00:57:55.064
And every time I rest my feet,
I'll think of Blaine.


